OL,4,CCovid: #13.5bn needed to help pupils
OL,5,Ccatch up, report says
OL,6, Some #13.5bn is needed to reverse the
OL,7, damage to pupils' education caused by
OL,8, the pandemic, a think tank has said.
OL,10,FThe Education Policy Institute says the
OL,11,Fmoney is needed as pupils have lost up
OL,12,Fto two months of learning in reading,
OL,13,Fand up to three months in maths.
OL,15,FIt is calling on the government to
OL,16,Fextend the school day and increase
OL,17,Ffunding for poor pupils, as part of a
OL,18,Fseries of measures to help recovery.
OL,20,FThe government has already given #1.7bn
OL,21,Ffor catch-up support in England.
